title: Time: Addendum #1 - Dark (TV Series) God and Time
description:
Netflix is halfway through a four season German television series named Dark. What started as a murder mystery has muted into a time traveling interrogation of the nature of such tiny subjects as God and Time. Such subject matter would normally, in American series, be relegated to sentimentality, simple mindedness or irony. Such a show might be considered pretentious by the cynical. But this show delivers the goods. 

And as such easily makes a handy Addendum to my Time series. So dig in my friends. And while you're at it watch the series. 


My Time series begins here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dummRArTg60&list=PLJ895CQuvzeWUQEEg73MujIU86z7E7_Re

(I don't want to have to make my personal page private because I have too many 'friends'. If it's dialogue you want go there. I'll start 'community' page soon enough if the demand is there.) 

Thanks for watching, more coming soon! 

Meanwhile dig into the Anadromous past. Swim against the stream my friends. 

From Tbilisi Georgia (Look it up on a map!) 
Byrne
